==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Revivify
<hw>Re*viv"i*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>r⟦eacute⟧vivifier</ets>, L. <ets>revivificare</ets>. See
<er>Vivify</er>.]</ety> <def>To cause to revive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some association may <qex>revivify</qex> it enough to make it
flash, after a long oblivion, into consciousness.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W.
Hamilton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reviving</ent>⟦br⟧
